OL,3,CThames Water swings to profit but debt
OL,4,Cmountain swells to #20bn
OL,6,FTroubled Thames Water has revealed it
OL,7,Fswung to an annual profit but saw its
OL,8,Fdebt mountain balloon close to #20
OL,9,Fbillion.
OL,11,FThe UK's biggest water supplier, which
OL,12,Fhas around 16 million customers across
OL,13,FLondon and the South East, reported
OL,14,Fpre-tax profits of #226.4 million for
OL,15,Fthe year to March 31 in a marked
OL,16,Fimprovement from mammoth losses of
OL,17,F#1.65 billion the previous year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
