OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784107113
OL,3,CThames Water swings to profit but debt
OL,4,Cmountain swells to #20bn
OL,6,FBut full-year results showed the
OL,7,Fsupplier's debts swelled to #19.77
OL,8,Fbillion, up from #17.73 billion the
OL,9,Fprevious year as the group said it
OL,10,Fcontinued to draw down to fund capital
OL,11,Finvestment.
OL,13,FCreditors are battling to secure a
OL,14,Frescue deal for Thames Water after
OL,15,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,16,Flast month warned she did not believe
OL,17,Fthe plan for the stricken utility goes
OL,18,Ffar enough to protect customers or the
OL,19,Fenvironment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
