OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784107113
OL,3,CThames Water swings to profit but debt
OL,4,Cmountain swells to #20bn
OL,6,FIt came as a last-minute blow for
OL,7,Ftheir hopes of a deal to stave off
OL,8,Ftemporary renationalisation.
OL,10,FIndustry regulator Ofwat said to have
OL,11,Fbeen close to accepting the offer from
OL,12,Fbidding consortium London & Valley
OL,13,FWater, which has proposed injecting
OL,14,F#10 billion into debt-laden Thames
OL,15,FWater in return for any new fines over
OL,16,Fsewage leaks being waived for four
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,19,FThames Water said last month it had
OL,20,Fenough funding until September.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
