OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784107113
OL,3,CThames Water swings to profit but debt
OL,4,Cmountain swells to #20bn
OL,6,FChief executive Chris Weston said:
OL,7,F"Thames Water today is a very
OL,8,Fdifferent business from what it was
OL,9,Ftwo years ago.
OL,11,F"While we have a lot more to achieve,
OL,12,Fthe progress we have made in turning
OL,13,Fthe company around has meant we are
OL,14,Fnow performing better and are in a
OL,15,Fstrong position to accelerate the
OL,16,Fdelivery of the biggest upgrade of our
OL,17,Finfrastructure in 150 years."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784107113
OL,3,CThames Water swings to profit but debt
OL,4,Cmountain swells to #20bn
OL,6,F"The upgrade of our network requires a
OL,7,Fmaterial and sustained increase in
OL,8,Fcapital investment over the next
OL,9,Fdecade.
OL,11,F"This year we invested #2.7 billion, a
OL,12,F20% increase over last year, as we
OL,13,Finvested over #7 million every day to
OL,14,Fmodernise our water and wastewater
OL,15,Fnetworks. We've grown our workforce by
OL,16,F12% creating new jobs and vital youth
OL,17,Femployment opportunities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
