OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784107113
OL,3,CThames Water swings to profit but debt
OL,4,Cmountain swells to #20bn
OL,6,F"Every pound of profit is reinvested
OL,7,Fin the business to improve our
OL,8,Fperformance. Customer revenue does not
OL,9,Fcover our required expenditure and our
OL,10,Fcash outflow before new debt funding
OL,11,Fwas #1.1bn."
OL,13,FHe added: "While operationally the
OL,14,Fbusiness is improving, we are also
OL,15,Fworking with our creditors, regulators
OL,16,Fand Government to complete our
OL,17,Frecapitalisation."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
